    public static interface TypeList.Generic
extends FilterableList<TypeDescription.Generic,TypeList.Generic>
    A list containing descriptions of generic types.

      • asTokenList

        ByteCodeElement.Token.TokenList<TypeVariableToken> asTokenList(ElementMatcher<? super TypeDescription> visitor)
        Transforms a list of attached type variables into their tokenized form. Calling this method throws an IllegalStateException if any type in this list does not represent a type variable (TypeDefinition.Sort.VARIABLE).
        参数:
        visitor - The visitor to use for detaching the type variable's bounds.
        返回:
        A list of tokens representing the type variables contained in this list.

        返回:
        A list of the types returned by the supplied visitor.
